channel.title: Private Server Crashes
channel.description:
Hello. I'm have a problem with a private server I'm trying to set up. I downloaded the client/source and the Java thing already. Whenever I run the server and click two times, it just closes. I've tried many other clients/sources, but it always ends up with the same result. Could someone please help me? I also know it's not my computer, because I've set up a private server on this computer before a long time ago. :(

item.description:

I’ve tried many other clients/sources, but it always ends up with the same result. Could someone please help me?
